snippet.textDisplay: What an absolute waste of time..mine for watching and theirs for producing this..I see absolutely no quality in this fusion. There was no harmony in the tune, everybody was performing their own piece. Everything looked very jumbled up. Rap was absolutely no fun and very poorly written. What I fail to understand is that how does rappers get the right of being discourteous and disparaging in their writings just because it’s a rap. Take cue from people around the world who make fusion music and invest some time learning the craft before actually making something like this please. I saw Ravi Kishan’s piece on Facebook and was actually excited to see this video. In the end all’s a big dud..
